  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe pain (VAS &gt; or = 60mm); injuries of the leg, ankle or foot

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hypersensitivity to student agents

          -  Local infection

          -  Nerve or vascular pathology in the affected limb, coagulation pathology,

          -  Chronic use of opoids, use of opoids within 6 hours

          -  Drug addiction

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Systolic blood pressure less than 90 mmHg

          -  Respiratory rate less than 16 per minute

          -  Glasgow coma scale &lt; 14.
      </textblock>
